<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Motorcycle Accessories Audit Dashboard</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #0f172a;
            color: #e2e8f0;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: auto;
            padding: 40px 20px;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #38bdf8;
        }
        h2 {
            color: #22c55e;
        }
        .card {
            background: #1e293b;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
        }
        ul {
            padding-left: 20px;
        }
        li {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #94a3b8;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">
    <h1>🏍️ Motorcycle Accessories Audit Dashboard</h1>

    <div class="card">
        <h2>📌 Project Overview</h2>
        <p>
            This project is an Audit Dashboard designed for a motorcycle accessories shop to monitor 
            sales, inventory, and overall business performance in real-time.
        </p>
        <p>
            The dashboard helps shop owners make data-driven decisions by providing clear insights 
            into revenue trends, stock levels, and product performance.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
        <h2>🚀 Key Features</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>📊 Sales and revenue tracking</li>
            <li>📦 Inventory monitoring with stock alerts</li>
            <li>🔍 Product performance analysis</li>
            <li>📈 Trend visualization for better decision-making</li>
            <li>⚡ Interactive and user-friendly interface</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
        <h2>🎯 Objective</h2>
        <p>
            The main goal of this dashboard is to improve operational efficiency, reduce stock issues, 
            and enhance overall business performance using data analytics.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
        <h2>🛠️ Use Case</h2>
        <p>
            This dashboard can be used by shop owners and managers to quickly analyze sales patterns, 
            identify fast-moving and slow-moving products, and ensure effective inventory management.
        </p>
    </div>

    <footer>
        <p>Built for learning & real-world business insights 🚀</p>
    </footer>
</div>

</body>
</html>
